<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Portfolio | lisAIconsulting</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --accent: #3b82f6;
      --text: #111827;
      --text-muted: #4b5563;
      --border: #e5e7eb;
      --bg-soft: #f7f9fc;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background: #fff;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    h1, h2, h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .page-section {
      padding: 3.5rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .section-soft {
      background: var(--bg-soft);
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .container.narrow {
      max-width: 800px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .intro {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .portfolio-item {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    }

    .portfolio-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .tag {
      background: #eef4ff;
      color: var(--accent);
      padding: 0.4rem 0.7rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .item-summary {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .summary-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .info-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
      background: #fbfcfe;
    }

    .two-column {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .content-block {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .workflow-box {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      background: #f8fafc;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      max-width: 420px;
    }

    .workflow-step {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 0.75rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .workflow-arrow {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0.4rem 0;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .clean-list {
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
    }

    .image-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .image-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 0.75rem;
      background: #fbfcfe;
    }

    .image-card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 200px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: #fff;
    }

    .image-card figcaption {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .cta {
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 0.7rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .summary-grid,
      .image-grid,
      .two-column {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">Portfolio</p>
      <h1>Selected Work</h1>
      <p class="intro">
        This page highlights practical examples of delivery, automation, and structured execution.
        The goal is to show how business needs can be translated into clear workflows,
        working artifacts, and measurable operational improvement.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section section-soft">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="portfolio-item">

        <div class="portfolio-header">
          <div>
            <h2>Defect Tracking Automation (n8n)</h2>
          </div>
          <span class="tag">Workflow Automation</span>
        </div>

        <p class="item-summary">
          A lightweight workflow automation designed to improve how teams capture,
          organize, and track defects using structured intake and centralized logging.
        </p>

        <div class="summary-grid">
          <div class="info-card">
            <h3>Problem</h3>
            <p>
              Teams rely on scattered communication and manual tracking, resulting in inconsistent intake and limited visibility.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="info-card">
            <h3>Solution</h3>
            <p>
              Built an automated intake workflow using n8n integrated with a form and Google Sheets for centralized tracking.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="info-card">
            <h3>Outcome</h3>
            <p>
              Improved visibility, reduced manual effort, and created a consistent defect tracking process.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="two-column">
          <div class="content-block">
            <h3>Workflow Overview</h3>
            <p>
              The workflow captures defect submissions, processes them through automation,
              and logs them into a centralized tracking system.
            </p>

            <div class="workflow-box">
              <div class="workflow-step">User submits form</div>
              <div class="workflow-arrow">↓</div>
              <div class="workflow-step">n8n workflow triggered</div>
              <div class="workflow-arrow">↓</div>
              <div class="workflow-step">Data processed</div>
              <div class="workflow-arrow">↓</div>
              <div class="workflow-step">Logged to Google Sheet</div>
              <div class="workflow-arrow">↓</div>
              <div class="workflow-step">Team visibility</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="content-block">
            <h3>What This Demonstrates</h3>
            <ul class="clean-list">
              <li>Workflow automation design</li>
              <li>Process improvement</li>
              <li>Centralized tracking</li>
              <li>Business-to-technical translation</li>
              <li>Deliverable-focused execution</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h3>Sample Screens</h3>

          <div class="image-grid">
            <figure class="image-card">
              <img src="/images/portfolio/workflow.png" alt="workflow" />
              <figcaption>n8n workflow</figcaption>
            </figure>

            <figure class="image-card">
              <img src="/images/portfolio/form.png" alt="form" />
              <figcaption>Defect intake form</figcaption>
            </figure>

            <figure class="image-card">
              <img src="/images/portfolio/sheet.png" alt="sheet" />
              <figcaption>Tracking output</figcaption>
            </figure>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="cta">
      <h2>Interested in Similar Work?</h2>
      <p>
        lisAIconsulting supports organizations that need practical help with AI programs,
        automation, and delivery execution.
      </p>
      <a class="button" href="/contact">Contact Me</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
